text: Donacea or Donakea () was an ancient town on the island of Tenos. It is mentioned in ancient inscriptions.IG XII 5, test. 1516.3; IG XII,5 872. Its site is tentatively located near Livada. ==References== Category:Populated places in the ancient Aegean islands Category:Former populated places in Greece Category:Tinos
title: Donacea
